      "char_offset_start": 0,
      "char_offset_end": 320,
      "exact_quote": "Bubble Sort la thuat toan sap xep don gian dua tren so sanh. Thuat toan hoat dong bang cach lap di lap lai qua danh sach, so sanh cac phan tu lien ke va hoan doi chung neu chung khong dung thu tu. Do phuc tap: O(n2) thoi gian, O(1) khong gian. Day la thuat toan khong hieu qua cho danh sach lon nhung de hieu va cai dat.",
